                  "content": "3. Why Do We Process Your Personal Data?",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "UlMu9",
                  "name": "pps3t1",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "3.1 To open and maintain your account.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "1zaKB",
                  "name": "pps3t2",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "3.2 To operate shipping and customer support.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "iSfiU",
              "name": "pps4",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 24,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "0ymdj",
                  "name": "pps4h",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "content": "4. How Can You Exercise Your Data Subject Rights?",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "9Ywug",
                  "name": "pps4intro",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "Under certain circumstances, you have the following rights under data protection laws:",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "puuHD",
                  "name": "pps4r1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon_font",
                      "id": "Jr6YH",
                      "name": "pps4r1dot",
                      "width": 0,
                      "height": 0,
                      "iconFontName": "circle-dot",
                      "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                      "fill": "#0F766E"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ufAB8",
                      "name": "pps4r1t",
                      "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                      "content": "Right to access, correct, or erase your personal data to verify lawful processing and request correction or deletion where applicable.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Wx4xC",
                  "name": "pps4r2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon_font",
                      "id": "Ds7ud",
                      "name": "pps4r2dot",
                      "width": 0,
                      "height": 0,
                      "iconFontName": "circle-dot",
                      "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                      "fill": "#0F766E"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "wNEjb",
                      "name": "pps4r2t",
                      "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                      "content": "Right to object to processing of your personal data where we rely on legitimate interest.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "xKxFz",
                  "name": "pps4r3",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon_font",
                      "id": "eutLB",
                      "name": "pps4r3dot",
                      "width": 0,
                      "height": 0,
                      "iconFontName": "circle-dot",
                      "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                      "fill": "#0F766E"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "B7MCq",
                      "name": "pps4r3t",
                      "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                      "content": "Right to request restriction of processing, including when data accuracy is disputed or retention is needed for legal claims.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "0I0XZ",
                  "name": "pps4r4",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon_font",
                      "id": "ocEl0",
                      "name": "pps4r4dot",
                      "width": 0,
                      "height": 0,
                      "iconFontName": "circle-dot",
                      "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                      "fill": "#0F766E"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "NdA5D",
                      "name": "pps4r4t",
                      "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                      "content": "Right to request transfer of your personal data to you or a third party.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "PEDPo",
                  "name": "pps4r5",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon_font",
                      "id": "PA6YP",
                      "name": "pps4r5dot",
                      "width": 0,
                      "height": 0,
                      "iconFontName": "circle-dot",
                      "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                      "fill": "#0F766E"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "LbOzF",
                      "name": "pps4r5t",
                      "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                      "content": "Right to withdraw consent at any time where processing is based on consent.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "SRT21",
                  "name": "pps4contact",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "To exercise your rights, contact us at coincart@coincart.store. We try to respond within one month.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "HBHsp",
              "name": "pps5",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 24,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Hfp0A",
                  "name": "pps5h",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "content": "5. How Long Do We Keep Your Personal Data?",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "4SgBz",
                  "name": "pps5t1",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "We keep personal data for as long as needed to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected, including selling products and protecting our, your, or others' interests.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "itegL",
                  "name": "pps5t2",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "If you have an account with us, we keep account-activity data while the account exists.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ABPuV",
                  "name": "pps5t3",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "We keep tax-relevant information for a minimum of 7 years.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "UklO7",
              "name": "pps6",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 24,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "J33Ni",
                  "name": "pps6h",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "content": "6. Minors",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "owzsR",
                  "name": "pps6t1",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "Our website and services are not intended for children under 16 years of age.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "hIpsq",
                  "name": "pps6t2",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If we learn we have collected personal data from a child under 16 without verified parental consent, we will delete that information.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "nFstY",
              "name": "pps7",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 24,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "tB3lR",
                  "name": "pps7h",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "content": "7. Miscellaneous",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "xFDUf",
                  "name": "pps7t1",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "7.1 If you have questions about this Privacy Policy and how we handle your data, email coincart@coincart.store.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "xcVXp",
                  "name": "pps7t2",
                  "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                  "content": "7.2 As our platform evolves, we may modify this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be made on this page and, when significant, we will inform you.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "LK7Or",
